		<td bgcolor="#DEDACB">
	
			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Hey<BR>
I just discovered a good thing to do to powerlevel. Go to SRo and camp the druid ruins. Everyso often, a druid will pop by. Ask him NICELY or even pay him for a skin spell, a regeneration, and a damage shield. When you got them, pop on Sow. Now run like crazy and find things to kill. Things will fall easily because of your regen and your damage shield. Just attack anything and heal yourself if your low. Try running into orc camps and letting the orcs kill themselves. BUT if you want the xp and the loot, you have to hit the mob by at least ONE hp. If the damage shield runs out, ask another druid NICELY for another one. I'm getting a LOT of levels like this. Enjoy!<BR>
<BR>
Majin, 12th circle shaman. MAJIN DA BEST!
